{"tid":981534,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"樂迷有福了 可以現場聽到呢幾首神曲！！！","createTime":"2019-01-14T11:17:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-17T02:48:01.000Z","uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b184428f5ff9fcb0207576fa1790b8ad86ebab25","tid":981534,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T11:17:24.000Z","msg":"參加無綫歌唱節目《超級巨聲》入行的藝人陳國峰（Penny）舉行首個個唱發布會，他受訪時坦言心情緊張，問到如何促成是次個唱？他表示：「要多謝《流行經典50年》，多謝家燕姐（薛家燕）同小田哥（黎小田），我上咗去節目後有好大回響，於是有人搵我開今次個唱。我入行差不多10年，一直做住同唱歌無關嘅嘢。（個唱有咩特別表演？）希望抽到時間去排舞，由細到大都好鍾意郭富城，想向佢致敬，所以會跳唱佢嘅勁歌熱舞。我會盡量練好啲，睇吓搵唔搵到郭富城嘅排舞師Sunny Wong去排舞。（會唔會請郭富城嚟睇？）我都想，試過搵，但未必得，佢可能太忙。（到時會唔會騷肌？）大家會唔會睇到厭？如果大家想睇，徇眾要求下我可以除。」 <br />\n<br />\nPenny指入行以來<span style=\"color: red;\">出過4首兒歌，笑言會在演唱會上唱這幾首代表作</span>，而一眾《兄弟幫》的主持也會上台助陣：「佢哋好鍾意跳舞，上次我哋一齊上船登台都係唱郭富城嘅《對你愛不完》，就係由林盛斌負責排舞，我哋好認真，每個動作都研究咗好耐。（會唔會想請家燕姐？）會請佢嚟睇。（請佢上台跳十字舞？）當日好隨意，因為舞台同觀眾席近，隨時可以請佢哋上台。」 <br />\n<br />\n兩首高達主題曲 無睇過套野 都一定聽過首歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_AzlqWuWCcg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_AzlqWuWCcg&d=e3TO9ons5iEXHyTzMAd6wdibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=951e7c76\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_AzlqWuWCcg</a><br />\n如身邊有你 永遠跟你一塊 我哪會孤單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當然唔少得 佢另一首更加膾炙人口既首本名曲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">無</span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">窮</span></span><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">扯</span></span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">無</span></span><span style=\"color: blue;\">盡</span> <span style=\"color: blue;\">無</span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">窮</span></span><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">扯</span></span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">無</span></span><span style=\"color: blue;\">盡</span><br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/z3gPjFcHGcg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fz3gPjFcHGcg&d=e3TO9ons5iEXHyTzMAd6wdibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=9292394b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/z3gPjFcHGcg</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a47d6148e56b281bcda857fd5325bf4fd2c9a477","tid":981534,"uid":115189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T02:18:09.000Z","msg":"好難唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0e81c55ac27c04d52a704fbef25a7b5774088c1","tid":981534,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a47d6148e56b281bcda857fd5325bf4fd2c9a477","tid":981534,"uid":115189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T02:18:09.000Z","msg":"好難唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T02:24:35.000Z","msg":"仲有rap<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"519a5d3575eeaa0a6cdf29e38bb1074ae35ed2f3","tid":981534,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T02:48:01.000Z","msg":"屌, 原來係呢條撚樣唱, 好撚難聽"}]}